{"tid":410456,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]扑野終極上訴獲批准，絕對責任受質疑","createTime":"2017-09-23T03:01:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-23T07:01:19.000Z","uid":389,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3fb4e0e61b4b55cd0101a9182a9852766f6b7e66","tid":410456,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T03:01:12.000Z","msg":"港大男生在互聯網上認識自稱17歲的援交女，二人共浴及口交，惟事後少女父親告發少女只得13歲，港大生被控非禮。港大生曾指女童「有前有後」，外表全無稚氣，真誠地相信她已過16歲。裁判官原先判他無罪，律政司上訴至高院，高院再將他定罪。港大生申請上訴至終院，今（22日）獲高院批准，指本案涉重大法律爭議。<br />\n<br />\n被告蔡偉麟，24歲，被控2014年暑假時，非禮當時只得13歲的援交少女，蔡與少女在成人網站接洽，少女寄給他一張半身照，二人其後相約到時鐘酒店開房，蔡對少女上下其手，少女亦為他口交，蔡事後給對方1千元肉金。<br />\n非禮罪是否涉「絕對責任」成爭議<br />\n<br />\n本案的爭議在於，現行法例中與未滿16歲少女發年性行為，屬「絕對責任」罪行，即控方毋須證明被告是否「真誠相信」女童未成年，即只要與未成年女童性交，即屬違法。但非禮罪則沒有相關原則。蔡聲稱深信女事主已經17歲，控方卻認為蔡不能以「真誠相信」援交少女童年齡已超過16歲作為抗辯理由。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/121049?utm_content=buffer42f4a&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=facebook+hk01&amp;utm_campaign=buffer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fsns%2Farticle%2F121049%3Futm_content%3Dbuffer42f4a%26utm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%2Bhk01%26utm_campaign%3Dbuffer&d=J856HIiPruNH7HKwC4Wa2Gxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=0368e814\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/121049?utm_content=buffer42f4a&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=facebook+hk01&amp;utm_campaign=buffer</a>"},{"pid":"f3f3ab36d8361a67275810fc9c254269b72abe3b","tid":410456,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T03:11:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n這些機會..."},{"pid":"0dbefcae322e02c9399d7ef762cf20c4e22630fc","tid":410456,"uid":32380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T03:12:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal